00:02:54.766 --> 00:02:55.965
So the decline slows,

00:02:55.965 --> 00:02:57.550
it becomes less negative

00:02:57.550 --> 00:03:00.597
as we approach the temperature
of the refrigerator.

00:03:00.597 --> 00:03:02.568
So you have this. . . .

00:03:02.568 --> 00:03:07.568
